data.description: MOVE-IN READY HOME AT THE HAMMOCKS AT WESTPORT W/LAKE VIEW- Don't wait to build, check out this move-in ready, meticulously cared for, lakefront home w/ ~$10,000 in updates/upgrades. Home features the desirable Fiesta floor plan offering 3 large bedrooms including a spacious master retreat plus two private guest rooms sharing a guest bath. The large foyer greets you as you enter the home welcoming you to the open concept living space. Wide open layout begins w/the contemporary kitchen continuing through a charming dining area onto the main living room. Living room opens to a screened lanai. The kitchen is exceptional w/quartz counters, Shaker-style wood cabinetry, closet pantry & stainless-steel appliances. The kitchen island features a large split sink & breakfast bar seating. The adjacent dining area is perfect for hosting friends & family. Architectural features include a neutral yet nautical color palate with cooling whites & blues intermingled w/greys and tans that come from the contemporary flooring. Floor tones include a driftwood-inspired, wood-look, plank tile flooring that runs throughout the main living area & bathrooms plus greige carpet in the bedrooms. The living room opens to the lanai which runs the length of the back & features a brick paver deck that is partially screened & partially open air - perfect for grilling AND relaxing outside while enjoying the lakeview. Private master retreat offers a spa-like, en-suite master bath w/quartz counters, tiled & glass-enclosed shower, private WC & an oversized, walk-in closet. Other amenities include hurricane protection, lake-fed irrigation system, an attached two-car garage & large laundry room with INCLUDED W/D that doubles as a mudroom w/access to the garage. ~$10,000 IN UPDATES INCLUDE: added gutters, extended back patio by 14x8 open air area w/brick paver deck, NEW blinds & ceiling fans in every bedroom, the main living room & the lanai and washer/dryer. Home comes with a 10 YEAR TRANSFERABLE STRUCTURAL WARRANTY (around 8 years remaining). Additionally, this home is grandfathered out of the new required increased M/I HOA fee of ~$250/quarter. The Hammocks at West Port is a growing community in Port Charlotte w/a great location. Take advantage of all that the area has to offer including quick access to all of the shopping, dining & medical facilities in both Port Charlotte & North Port. Enjoy nearby Centennial Park that features a multi-purpose gymnasium with six basketball goals, lined for four pickleball courts and two volleyball courts, two multi-purpose rooms, a fitness center and a community garden. The outdoor facilities include a 50-meter Olympic-size pool w/diving well, four lighted baseball fields, a softball field, colorful playground and four soccer fields. The park also offers a challenging 18-hole disc golf course. Close to numerous nature parks, Charlotte Sports Park (home of Tampa Bay Rays Spring training) & several area beaches including Englewood, Venice & Boca Grande. Make an appointment today. You won't be disappointed.
